{
  "stem": "23410.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, nobody-- the son did not know, either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came in the next night and told us a story right in the-- we were in the stables, upstairs in the stable.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was laying in one place, and [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] was-- Moishe [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] was on the other side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told to Moishe [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They did not even speak to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, a kid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's a kid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he told him that this what his daughter-in-law told him, and he wants him to take him to-- to his basement.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he has in the night, like to escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the daughter-in-law or his son does not know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They never told his son, because he was a heavy drinker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, but--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that he will-- you know, if you drink heavy, you sometimes talk out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you don't know, you don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you know, then heavy drinking can-- and he said, in the night, I will come, and you will escape from here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I will come next morning and speak to my daughter-in-law and ask about you and save these people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not know anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did not think about anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we were-- in the night, we walked out with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He took us to his place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I did not even know where I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the funny thing is, in the night, he-- Moishe [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] said, you know, in meantime, he found out that I don't have anything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he needs support, too, and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, in the night he felt-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he told Mr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Kalwinski, he is a baby.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
